const API_BASE_URL='/api';export const searchAPI={performSearch:async(term,startDate,endDate)=>{try{const url=new URL("".concat(API_BASE_URL,"/search"));url.searchParams.append('term',term);if(startDate)url.searchParams.append('startDate',startDate);if(endDate)url.searchParams.append('endDate',endDate);const response=await fetch(url);if(!response.ok)throw new Error('Failed to fetch');return await response.json();}catch(error){console.error('Search failed:',error);throw error;}}};
